Package: lmn-gpo
Version: 1.0.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Kevin Stenzel <kevin@ks98.de>
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-yaml, python3-samba, samba-common-bin, openssl
Homepage: https://github.com/faircomp/linuxmuster-gpo-template
Description: Windows Group Policy toolkit for linuxmuster.net (Samba AD DC)
 lmn-gpo builds, links and permissions Windows 11 Group Policy Objects directly
 on the linuxmuster.net 7.x Samba Active Directory domain controller, without the
 Windows GPMC. It ships a declarative YAML catalog (privacy, lockdown, KMS,
 branding, Firefox, proxy, WLAN, Veyon, boot order, time sync and more), is
 multi-school capable and idempotent, and includes a setup assistant, a doctor
 environment check, a self-test and a dry-run mode.
